{"tid":1308582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到而家都冇人有說服力解釋到連儂牆有咩問題，但星期六日遊行日就真係唔好做","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:14:52.000Z","uid":31215,"like":13,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"790971fbd034d2283ab82b4014d966d4bf66bfc3","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"我係支持連儂牆嘅<br />\n講下意見先<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人話失焦五大訴求<br />\n成牆都好多人寫五大訴求點樣失焦法？<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人話影響抗爭<br />\n抗爭同連儂牆有咩衝突先<br />\n我星期一至五連儂牆<br />\n星期六日遊行甚至佔領得唔得<br />\n我地唔係犧牲抗爭嘅時間整牆<br />\n係犧牲平時打機睇片嘅時候整囉好冇<br />\n你有其他意見，選舉好、deadline 好、登報好<br />\n一樣有人討論有人做<br />\n<br />\n3. 有人話守牆問題<br />\n根本冇人守<br />\n係幅牆時時刻刻都有十幾二十人圍觀<br />\n寫張紙都2-3分鐘啦<br />\n呢個時候有一個藍絲衝過黎<br />\n可以想像到大家都會屌9佢而唔係二十人一齊落荒而逃<br />\n咁一屌咪衝突，有衝突咪有機會受傷<br />\n根本唔係想守牆，而係衝突係難以避免<br />\n你鼓勵大家制服佢，現實過叫全部寫緊野睇緊野嘅人一見人黎就走<br />\n<br />\n4. 有人話冇意思<br />\n我覺得連儂牆係幾有意思<br />\n連儂牆有啲似做地區工作，散播思想<br />\n好多街坊得個睇字<br />\n唔係深黃<br />\n你遞支筆俾佢佢有寫埋一份<br />\n近來氣氛好沉重好多人絕望<br />\n其實喺好近自己嘅地方有啲牆係好好<br />\n可以互相打氣，又抒發下，見下其他同路人<br />\n真係有好好嘅情緒幫助<br />\n仲可以增加社會不確定性<br />\n冇人知邊個位幾時有衝突<br />\n帶來輕微動蕩提升管治成本<br />\n<br />\n5. 有人話雨革都係咁而失敗<br />\n雨革失敗係只做左膠野<br />\n忘記左抗爭<br />\n而家抗爭都排哂程<br />\n排到八月<br />\n係中間啲時間做下左膠野<br />\n情況有唔同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於以上面我係支持繼續整嘅<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;分隔線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n但遊行日真係唔好整<br />\n會分薄左人<br />\n就算你唔出去遊行都唔好整<br />\n會吸引其他人幫手<br />\n令佢地覺得就算冇去遊行都參與左場運動<br />\n用一個廉價行為代替左遊行<br />\n所以遊行同日只有遊行<br />\n沒有其他任何事"},{"pid":"7b7996c2c046eb65bcf25e5f37b88b6e8c405597","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5da0af5cdc1c3c1c4c936940a09e6fcf9e69d2a","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7a73a2c3005b5f35833c5c8ca34a8bb709d7df4d","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"dae460d0b9b012b79d49360d50fcc40723258609","tid":1308582,"uid":173814,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"做你自己想做既野，由其他人都一樣<br />\n想行咪行，關你差事？"},{"pid":"26524f776036d997583710eb0c31cac81f44bee8","tid":1308582,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"佢堆全部都係3毛挑起大家對罵，唔駛咁上心"},{"pid":"3d65ca7e725684f0afb2b4a770e70a73e76041d4","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dae460d0b9b012b79d49360d50fcc40723258609","tid":1308582,"uid":173814,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"做你自己想做既野，由其他人都一樣<br />\n想行咪行，關你差事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"冇人叫人唔好行喎<br />\n我叫人唔好再打擊連儂牆<br />\n但星期六日有遊行就唔好搞牆<br />\n你閱讀理解拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb5300da46a053ab8dac09d38c6c945ca4a079","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26524f776036d997583710eb0c31cac81f44bee8","tid":1308582,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"佢堆全部都係3毛挑起大家對罵，唔駛咁上心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"啲post係咁詆毀連儂牆<br />\n但根本冇說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6675a563f1506d388aeb18d4b41fdbb820abcb3b","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"負評我又唔講理據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff642919ddbad9385231058dc252cbb873ce7d8","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"淨係識負評<br />\n又唔解釋清楚連儂牆問題何在<br />\n個個一黎就jump to conclusion 會影響抗爭<br />\n中間個推論都唔成理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a175e6958c9174748af62deb9a6e5523fcf0a3","tid":1308582,"uid":255992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"[突發]星期六各區大部份巴士臨時取消前往北區運動場巴士站!?點撚算?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308611</a>"},{"pid":"c1baddf3882242e83c6fa695ae3e6171330b5ced","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2552722294f9577b2681a7e12292e33199c7a69a","tid":1308582,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ff642919ddbad9385231058dc252cbb873ce7d8","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"淨係識負評<br />\n又唔解釋清楚連儂牆問題何在<br />\n個個一黎就jump to conclusion 會影響抗爭<br />\n中間個推論都唔成理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"我負評你條戇鳩話遊行無用嘅"},{"pid":"976ca332097c8fd39e733171f02883b20db96d68","tid":1308582,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feb0f9aee9585ff29c43a5ee22ec57f32362d557","tid":1308582,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b535fd597827c38426cb8bde70afc3681198580","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2552722294f9577b2681a7e12292e33199c7a69a","tid":1308582,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ff642919ddbad9385231058dc252cbb873ce7d8","tid":1308582,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"淨係識負評<br />\n又唔解釋清楚連儂牆問題何在<br />\n個個一黎就jum